This directory contains the postscript images of the contents
of the paper An interior point algorithm for nonlinear quantile
regression by R Koenker  and BJ Park.  The files are as follows

nlrq.ps		body of paper
title.ps	title page
appendix.ps	appendix of descriptions of test problems
table51.ps	test problem results
table52.ps	test problem results
alg.ps		S+ code for algorithm
out.ps		is the paper bits catted together for LJ Wei 5/01
